msgstr "Autorizar com %s"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2515
#: includes/crms/salesforce/admin/class-admin.php:74
#. Translators: %s is the name of the CRM.
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You'll be taken to %s to authorize WP Fusion and generate access keys for "
"this site."
msgstr ""
"Você será levado a %s para autorizar o WP Fusion e gerar chaves de acesso "
"para este site."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2519
#: includes/crms/salesforce/admin/class-admin.php:78
#, php-format
msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> Your site is not currently SSL secured "
"(https://). You will not be able to connect to the %s API. Your Site "
"Address must be set to https:// in Settings &raquo; General."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aviso:</strong> Seu site não está atualmente protegido por SSL "
"(https://). Você não poderá se conectar à API do %s. O endereço do seu site "
"deve estar configurado para https:// em Configurações &raquo; Geral."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2546
#. Translators: %s is the name of the CRM.
#, php-format
msgid "Connected to %s"
msgstr "Conectado ao %s"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2549
